I had it before.

87
00:06:18,378 --> 00:06:19,289
Morning.

88
00:06:19,290 --> 00:06:21,085
Early in the day for that.

89
00:06:21,086 --> 00:06:23,849
One for you, Happy New Year.

90
00:06:23,850 --> 00:06:26,739
