00:55:56,409 --> 00:55:58,802
No, no, please god, no!

1119
00:55:58,803 --> 00:56:00,386
No, no, no, no, no!

1120
00:56:05,480 --> 00:56:07,696
Don't, no, no, no!

1121
00:56:07,697 --> 00:56:08,947
Oh god, no, no!

