deal, but it didn't happen.

1243
01:02:13,880 --> 01:02:15,480
And Ron could testify to that.

1244
01:02:17,120 --> 01:02:19,389
Well Ron's not gonna testify.

1245
01:02:19,390 --> 01:02:21,029
Why not?

1246
