to worry about, I promise.

1259
01:03:10,998 --> 01:03:12,508
Hello?

1260
01:03:12,509 --> 01:03:15,918
Marilyn, hi, it's me.

1261
01:03:19,700 --> 01:03:20,700
How are you?

1262
01:03:23,377 --> 01:03:24,377
I'm doing okay.

1263
01:03:25,880 --> 01:03:27,460
