1264
01:03:27,461 --> 01:03:31,039
I just wanted to make
sure you were all right.

1265
01:03:31,040 --> 01:03:32,063
I'm just fine.

1266
01:03:36,798 --> 01:03:39,163
It wasn't me, Marilyn.

1267
01:03:42,510 --> 01:03:43,733
You know it wasn't me.

1268
